data.description: 4 bed 3 bath home in Moore with unique "mother-in-law" suite! 3cm granite in kitchen & bathroom. There is a breakfast bar in kitchen w/ LED lighting & bar stool seating, plenty of storage cabinets in hallway, large patio in backyard w/  French doors from living room & a unique bedroom suite (opposite of other bedrooms) with private mini-kitchen, built-in desk, & private full bath. Suite also has own door to backyard patio. Would be a perfect room for anyone needing a little more personal space! REPAIRS COMPLETED!  Seller is offering Home Warranty. Come make this your families  home!
